  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Project Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>· To assist Project Manager in co-ordination of Project management activities.</p>\n<p>· To handle project planning, site investigation, preliminary design and cost estimation</p>\n<p>· To undertake site surveys and set-out procedures for building projects.</p>\n<p>· To update pre-computation drawing when required.</p>\n<p>· To monitor and review sub-contractors' work to ensure contract specifications and performance standards are met.</p>\n<p>· Responsible for general site technical issue and other problems that may arise.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong>:</p>\n<p>•Diploma / Degree / in Civil Engineering or relevant certificate.</p>\n<p>•Minimum basic Autocad drafting knowledge.</p>\n<p>•Preferably has experience in Construction industry.</p>\n<p>•Fresh graduates are welcome to apply.</p>",
